FeedPackage.Summary:
Because your tests should be ridiculously easy to read and understand...
Sahara is an assertion library that lets you write your unit tests in a more natural language syntax. Sahara is also an auto-mocking framework that makes it easier to test and refactor legacy code by helping you isolate dependencies away from the classes you want to test.
